channel.title: Cabal Online
channel.description:
It's more of a game like WoW, but i think its like: Cabal > WoW, firstly because it's free, and secondly its Graphics are pretty decent, and thirdly it's still in Beta, So it's not just yet done with.
you can download it at: [url=http://ogplanet.com]http://ogplanet.com[/url] for Americans
[url=http://cabalonline.com]http://cabalonline.com[/url] for you Brit's
